success-story.name: KRITI GOEL, Angular Developer
success-story.content: Little did Abigail Washburn know that her life would forever change after she went to a party where she heard a record of traditional folk and bluegrass singer and flatpicking guitar player, Doc Watson singing Shady Grove.  She had what Frans Johansson dubs a click moment.
